data.description: This 1-story gem in The Bluffs at Canyon Springs is sure to please! Open concept with lots of natural light, ceramic tile, high ceilings, huge kitchen with island, Stainless-Steel Appliance package and walk in pantry includes front loader Washer/Dryer set. Primary bedroom is tucked away in the back of home with Garden Tub and Stand-Up Shower, not to mention the perfect closet space and ample storage. The guest wing has three additional bedrooms for the growing family, guest bathroom and more storage. This home sits on a big lot with a brand new fence, recently added Water Softener, Refrigerator and Microwave, and the Roof is 4 years young! Come out and see for yourself, you won't be disappointed!
